---
title: Soy Ginger Beef Patties with Roasted Broccoli Salad and Chili Peanut Dressing
description: Why did the pork patties cross the road? To get to the roasted broccoli salad party across the street! Zesty ginger and soy-infused pork patties are seared and served atop a playfully delicious and textural salad of mixed greens, roasted broccoli, crunchy peanuts, and shredded carrots in a piquant chili peanut dressing. It all gets finished with more dressing and scallion greens. Sorry, no more jokes, it’s time to eat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-ginger-beef-patties-2f0e352b.jpg
